          <p class="mt-5 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">Unless you tell us differently we provide three brands of dried food: Hills Science, Iams and Go-Cat, which are available at all times.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">Wet food is provided twice daily (sachets or foils, no tins unless you prefer).</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">Please advise of any special requirements. We like to follow your cat's home routine as closely as possible. It is in our best interest as well as your cat's to follow your instructions.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-cream rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <p class="font-display font-bold text-ink mb-3">What to bring</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-ink-soft text-sm">
