        <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">We want your pets to spend their time with us in contented ease, relaxed and laid back.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">If your cat likes to be groomed please bring your own brush or comb. Most cats like some attention and this is a great way to focus on them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
