          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🍲</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-3">Premium Food</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft text-sm leading-relaxed">Hills Science, Iams and Go-Cat dried food available at all times. Wet food twice daily.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-border text-center">
