          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-3">Personal Attention</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft text-sm leading-relaxed">We follow your cat's home routine as closely as possible, giving you complete peace of mind.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-border text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔒</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-3">Safe and Secure</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft text-sm leading-relaxed">A tranquil, comfortable and secure environment where your cat can relax and enjoy their stay.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
